room_title: Escape room "The Lost Jungle Safari" by Brainy Actz in San Diego
room_address: 10211 Pacific Mesa Blvd. Suite #409, San Diego CA, 92121
room_description: Deep in the jungles of Africa, your safari has taken an unfortunate wrong turn! As you frantically search for the way to safety, hints of an ancient treasure and a fierce native tribe begin to reveal themselves! Can you claim the treasure for yourselves before the natives turn you into stew?
